*Nevolju* je uništila njegovu karijeru. (Misfortune destroyed his career.)

*Nevolja* je bila nepredvidiva. (The trouble was unpredictable.)

On se često suočavao sa *nevoljama*. (He often faced troubles.)

On se nikada nije predavao u *nevolji*. (He never gave up in adversity.)

Ona je nosila *nevolje* drugima. (She carried troubles for others.)

*Nevoljama* je teško pobediti. (It's hard to overcome troubles.)